!! ## Language-independent flag diacritics

!! We have manually optimised the structure of our lexicon using following
!! flag diacritics to restrict morhpological combinatorics - only allow compounds
!! with verbs if the verb is further derived into a noun again:

!! | Flag | Explanation
!! | --- | --- 
! 20250901 F├Ėlgende flags udkommenteret, idet de tilsyneladende ikke bliver anvendt
! @P.NeedNoun.ON@    !!Ōēł |  @CODE@ | (Dis)allow compounds with verbs unless nominalised
! @D.NeedNoun.ON@    !!Ōēł |  @CODE@ | (Dis)allow compounds with verbs unless nominalised
! @C.NeedNoun@       !!Ōēł |  @CODE@ | (Dis)allow compounds with verbs unless nominalised

!! For languages that allow compounding, the following flag diacritics are needed
!! to control position-based compounding restrictions for nominals. Their use is
!! handled automatically if combined with +CmpN/xxx tags. If not used, they will
!! do no harm.

!! | Flag | Explanation
!! | --- | --- 
 !@P.CmpFrst.FALSE@ !!Ōēł |  @CODE@ | Require that words tagged as such only appear first
 !@D.CmpPref.TRUE@  !!Ōēł |  @CODE@ | Block such words from entering ENDLEX
 !@P.CmpPref.FALSE@ !!Ōēł |  @CODE@ | Block these words from making further compounds
 !@D.CmpLast.TRUE@  !!Ōēł |  @CODE@ | Block such words from entering R
 !@D.CmpNone.TRUE@  !!Ōēł |  @CODE@ | Combines with the next tag to prohibit compounding
 !@U.CmpNone.FALSE@ !!Ōēł |  @CODE@ | Combines with the prev tag to prohibit compounding
 !@P.CmpOnly.TRUE@  !!Ōēł |  @CODE@ | Sets a flag to indicate that the word has passed R
 !@D.CmpOnly.FALSE@ !!Ōēł |  @CODE@ | Disallow words coming directly from root.


!! Use the following flag diacritics to control downcasing of derived proper
!! nouns (e.g. Finnish Pariisi -> pariisilainen). See e.g. North S├Īmi for how to use
!! these flags. There exists a ready-made regex that will do the actual down-casing
!! given the proper use of these flags.

!! | Flag | Explanation
!! | --- | --- 
! @U.Cap.Obl@        !!Ōēł |  @CODE@ | Allowing downcasing of derived names: deatnulasj.
! @U.Cap.Opt@        !!Ōēł |  @CODE@ | Allowing downcasing of derived names: K├Ėbenhavn > k├Ėbenhavner.



